<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause"?><clause id="_be3965f8-8aea-4e04-b0be-0907f26df637" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="TAS"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>I18P4</sptc><title id="_40b2409f-951d-4ec9-b129-d5c6d63e06d2">Access</title><archive-num>2019: TAS H123 P3</archive-num><subclause id="_9ef6ee66-57df-4dcf-a234-8e97474b8e69" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_b53dd60c-97a9-490f-a587-8d5b4ec02400">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Access must be provided, to the degree necessary, to enable safe, equitable and dignified movement of people to and within a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2483_0.5.0.xml#_dcf88aaa-f959-470d-851a-80bf038bc603" id="_5d24c391-97cc-4210-b653-170cf8afc48a" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">temporary structure</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_3b744687-7b20-4377-a9db-5b64fb2576b1" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_60cd8b01-b357-4420-8e0c-f7b225b933c1">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>So that people can move safely to and within a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2483_0.5.0.xml#_dcf88aaa-f959-470d-851a-80bf038bc603" id="_afff3844-7d60-4e4c-9c50-35fa91e25400" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">temporary structure</xref>, it must haveâ€”</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_970ece38-6c7a-42dd-916d-7973380dfbb6">walking surfaces with safe gradients; and</li><li id="_eceedd52-f10e-4bc8-9185-1ababba4dd23">stairways and ramps with slip-resistant walking surfaces; and</li><li id="_d1865cdc-c474-4647-a671-64a167563785">suitable handrails where necessary to assist and provide stability to people using a stairway or ramp.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_0772299b-535f-4768-a2b3-1ce9faa66b10" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c0b85383-8274-4424-800a-9fb41e95aac5">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>Access for people with disabilities must be provided to and within a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2483_0.5.0.xml#_dcf88aaa-f959-470d-851a-80bf038bc603" id="_a0fd540b-fb07-4724-9fe8-b6a71c285841" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">temporary structure</xref>, including to any public sanitary facilities and all areas normally used by the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2480_0.4.0.xml#_98c47bc1-2d11-4c2d-8f0b-0534808fa254" id="_7ba742cf-ffb9-489a-a240-f7690d96ae50" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">public</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_f0acbb71-64ee-408c-bd2b-b0ad5a303474" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e2e05bd7-480e-44b8-8045-777dab89b681">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>If fixed seating is provided in a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2483_0.5.0.xml#_dcf88aaa-f959-470d-851a-80bf038bc603" id="_3564e2d4-d535-4377-804b-738853a60728" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">temporary structure</xref>, an appropriate number of wheelchair spaces must be provided.</p></subclause></clause>